Second, we investigate Scenario 2 with a higher intensity of global radiation. Also for this case, the qualitative outcome does not change, but again the price boundaries are of special interest. While the interval, in which all three long-run periodic solutions exist and the area of attraction is separated by an indifference threshold point, started at pF=0.0446\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
