				\begin{document}$${{ p}_{ F}}=0.0449$$\end{document}, a price at which in the original set a mixed portfolio just starts to be an alternative to the pure fossil one, not to mention Scenario 1 where this possibility does not exist at all at this price level. Starting at pF=0.0495\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
